# Project Standards

- This project uses `Next.js 16` App Router with `React 19`.
- Keep pages under `src/app` and colocate small route-specific components when useful.
- Prefer `next/image` for local images.
- Respect the styling pattern already used nearby, such as CSS Modules or existing classes.
- Follow the existing formatter settings: single quotes, semicolons, trailing commas, 2-space indentation, `printWidth` 120.
- Keep changes targeted and avoid unnecessary refactors.
- Check `AGENTS.md` for fuller project guidance when a task needs more context.
